<subSubSection id="BE6B89DD51743B1C795B5D1E592E55CE" pageId="0" pageNumber="83" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="47FC37A55B22D51F1A2FCA75A2AF0A5A" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B8C06D2699EC76FEA5A3B3CF9AD014EA" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">This species is named in honour of Dr Geoffrey Monteith, Emeritus Senior Curator, Queensland Museum, Brisbane, who was one of the collectors of one of the two known female specimens of this species.</paragraph>
<caption id="274B5670F157B2860EB798E2A9C5ABBA" doi="10.3897/zookeys.984.53587.figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/471315" pageId="0" pageNumber="83" start="Figure 9" startId="F9">
